
For Linux Ubuntu :

(1) Download latest version of Apache Jmeter from the link given below:
    http://jmeter.apache.org/download_jmeter.cgi

(2) Extract the Folder in the directory where you want to install it and it is done. No need of extra installation.

(3) To run the Jmeter GUI :
    (a) Go to the bin folder.
    (b) Run jmeter.sh (shell file) if there is any problem in execution then change the mode and make it executable.

(4) Example :
    > cd Documents/apache-jmeter-2.13/bin
    > ./jmeter.sh     (if error in execution run chmod +xX jmeter.sh before it).
